---
import Card from "./Card/index.astro";
import { SITE } from "../site-config";
---

<Card colSpan="md:col-span-1" rowSpan="md:row-span-6" title="About me">
  <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
    <p class="sr-only">
      Hi, I'm {SITE.author.firstName}, a petroleum engineer by day, full stack developer by passion, based in {SITE.location.countryName}.
      I build with JavaScript, React, Solidjs, Astro, Svelte, and Node.js, with an eye for SEO and UX/UI.
      At work, I bridge subsurface engineering and digital workflows &mdash; using Python, Spotfire, and Power BI to modernize how technical data drives decisions.
      Outside of it, I run a homelab (Proxmox, Docker, UniFi) where I tinker with networking, self-hosted services, and automation.
    </p>
    <div aria-hidden="true" class="text-sm font-light">
      <p>
        Hi, I'm {SITE.author.firstName} &mdash; a petroleum engineer by day, full stack developer by passion, based in {SITE.location.countryName}.
      </p>
      <p class="mt-2">
        I build with JavaScript, React, Solidjs, Astro, Svelte, and Node.js, with an eye for SEO and UX/UI.
      </p>
      <p class="mt-3">
        At work, I bridge subsurface engineering and digital workflows using Python, AI solutions and Power BI to modernize how technical data drives decisions.
      </p>
      </p>
      <p class="mt-4">
      Outside of it, I run a homelab (Proxmox, Docker, UniFi) where I tinker with networking, self-hosted services, AI and automation.
      </p>
  </div>
</Card>
